{"word":"G3356 - μετριοπαθέω - metriopathéō - met-ree-op-ath-eh'-o - Have compassion","slug":"G3356","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετριοπαθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>metriopathéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>met-ree-op-ath-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Have compassion"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - metriopatheo&#x0304;</b> - <i>met-ree-op-ath-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G3357\">G3357</a> and <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>; to <i>be moderate in passion</i>, that is, <i>gentle</i> (to <i>treat indulgently</i>): - have compassion."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>"}]}